1992   Hurricane Andrew                 US      74    30,000     16,500
1990   Winter gales                 Europe     230    15,000     10,000
1991   Floods                     PR China   3,074    15,000        410
1988   Earthquake                  Armenia  25,000    14,000          0
1994   LA earthquake                    US      59    30,000     10,000
1993   Floods                           US      41    12,000      1,000
