FT  28 DEC 94 / More trains for Channel tunnel
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The number of trains from London to Paris through the Channel tunnel is to
be doubled to four a day from next month, Eurostar said yesterday. From
January 23 four will leave London Waterloo International each day for Paris
and five on Fridays. Three will depart daily for Brussels.
